  <entry>
    <title>P9713 题解</title>
    <url>/2023/10/05/P9713/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>这里默认你已经看完题目。</p>
<p>做法呢，按题意直接模拟即可，每次把操作对应的 $x, y, z$ 减去输入的 $k$ 即可。</p>
<p>然后还要注意已经切完的部分不能再切了！！代码如下，注释写的很清楚了。</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> x, y, z, m;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    cin &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y &gt;&gt; z &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> mx, my, mz; <span class="comment">//当前以切去的部分</span></span><br><span class="line">    mx = my = mz = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (m--)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span> op, k;</span><br><span class="line">        cin &gt;&gt; op &gt;&gt; k;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (op == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (k &gt;= mx)  <span class="comment">//确保要切去的部分还没被切去</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                x -= (k - mx); <span class="comment">//已经切去的部分不能重复计算</span></span><br><span class="line">                mx = k;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (op == <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (k &gt;= my)  <span class="comment">//同上</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                y -= (k - my);</span><br><span class="line">                my = k;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (op == <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (k &gt;= mz)  <span class="comment">//同上</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                z -= (k - mz);</span><br><span class="line">                mz = k;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cout &lt;&lt; x * y * z &lt;&lt; endl; <span class="comment">//计算剩下的体积</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
